<HEADLINE>
FT  25 AUG 94 / Observer: Grilling
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
First, the Savoy hotel group halves the pay-out on its A shares, then Giles
Shepard, its managing director, emerges as catering adviser to the British
Army.
So is our next concern to be a halving of the peace dividend, a disgruntled
Savoy shareholder inquires.
