<HEADLINE>
FT  24 AUG 94 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Gold shares climbed off lows by the close to end little changed in a session
marked by a lack of news. The gold index shed 1 to 2,245, industrials gained
24 to 6,617 and the overall index added 11 to 5,858. De Beers slipped 20
cents to R109.80.
